� . . . Sure, you can come stay for . . . a bit.�  Peter�s eyebrows negotiated with Rebekkah�s gritted teeth - �For . . . as long as you need.  But realistically, how out of reach is an apartment for you?�
	�So it�s settled.� Rebekkah clapped her hands once deftly.  �How much longer do you need to be here?�
